{"tid":1394626,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 一群香港聖公會福利協會同工致香港市民的家書","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:19:37.000Z","uid":264904,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7e959c6415eca969e404bdbe7b8a7eca5af3b198","tid":1394626,"uid":264904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:08:58.000Z","msg":"致各位香港市民<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群來自香港聖公會福利協會的同工。<br />\n<br />\n香港素以治安良好，享有高度自由見稱，可惜由六月至今短短個多月，我們看到的俱是極端欺壓。七月二十一日晚上，警察於上環血腥鎮壓，無預警下在天橋向示威者開槍，並且瞄準示威者身體重要部位；另一邊廂，元朗地區發生黑社會暴力事件，一群白衣人士無差別地毆打市民，當中包括記者、議員、老人、小孩及孕婦，然而警察竟然未有即時派員阻止及控制場面，多段現場片段更顯示警黑勾結，妄顧市民生命。我們對此感到極度悲痛，悲的是政府對市民的五大訴求仍諸多推搪，未有正面回應；痛的是市民總要被警方以暴力方式對待，從催淚彈到布袋彈、橡膠子彈，從警棍、盾牌到白衣人的藤條、木棍。每週衝突，均以市民受傷告終。<br />\n<br />\n社會撕裂內訌，經歷多場大型遊行和抗議行動，甚至接連有市民選擇以死相諫，期望能夠喚醒政府回應民意，卻只換來港府冷待。就今日的社會局面，特首林鄭月娥實在難辭其咎。現時全港市民已經陷入崩潰邊緣。香港人不得不團結起來，每天交流自衛方法及尋找自保裝備，這一切，固然源於警察已經不再以保護市民為首要任務，但歸根究底全因港府無力管治。對此，身為福利協會工作者的我們向政府予以最嚴厲的譴責，並呼籲港府管治團隊要有承擔，正面回應五大訴求，當中獨立調查警黑合作及警隊濫權情況尤為迫切。<br />\n<br />\n我們不願再看到有香港人犧牲。對於政府的所作所為，我們感到極度羞恥，但作為香港一份子，我們會緊守崗位，為市民服務。面對社會上前所未見的動盪不安，香港人更要團結一致。我們亦希望所有香港人能夠勇於站出來，對抗暴政，與全港市民一同守護家園！<br />\n<br />\n一班來自香港聖公會福利協會不同單位的同工上<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GfdhdLu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGfdhdLu.png&h=67180f93&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AzTwxe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AzTwxe.png&h=8c47d9dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFWbich.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFWbich.png&h=84066df4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNVCYck.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNVCYck.png&h=504bc1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y3vvyLJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3vvyLJ.png&h=81ee4de2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uEd1FqM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuEd1FqM.png&h=e219f7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oymR2D9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoymR2D9.png&h=2cdeb02e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M36VKSx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM36VKSx.png&h=5dfc35cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdv7AZe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkdv7AZe.png&h=e1a5cbe8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e0250ad33de4d28584287278670c8772cdb1908","tid":1394626,"uid":260385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:11:17.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"cb334f7f4c6a08f36d213c421cfd6fb453ef31ed","tid":1394626,"uid":80128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:15:22.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"830b888dc584aa0dd5e0f72297ea259b6a32866e","tid":1394626,"uid":88922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:16:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56169c51d60d0bc5705cdef94c283380d17322b0","tid":1394626,"uid":80128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:19:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M7AfKV2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM7AfKV2.png&h=1737e754&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c5ff3a05e55bbc6b293551613cc9fe85c7bd653","tid":1394626,"uid":272081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:42:55.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"97ee439cf4840be82eba9d5d02c3817b2f8593c9","tid":1394626,"uid":288372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:48:13.000Z","msg":"願主憐憫"},{"pid":"2294a936147b7aa514128d2345f4bd78c9ea4e20","tid":1394626,"uid